"    <div class=\"reference\">",
"    </div>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 476px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Heel-pocket-out method to put on compression stockings",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 456px; height: 611px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    The heel-pocket-out method to put on compression stockings is as follows:",
"    <br>",
"     <ol>",
"      <li>",
"       Turn the leg part of the stocking inside-out down to the heel (as shown in A).",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       Put your foot into the stocking, hold onto the folded edge, and pull the stocking onto your foot and over the heel (as shown in B).",
"      </li>",
"      <li>",
"       Gently work the stocking up your leg by turning it right-side out (as shown in C).",
"      </li>",
"     </ol>",
"     <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"     </div>",
"     <div class=\"reference\">",
"     </div>",
"    </br>",
"   </div>",
"  </div>",
" </div>",
